data.description: Welcome to Fountain Springs in Plantation. Great location! This 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home is ready to meet its new owner. Featuring an open great room upon entry with volume ceilings and windows to let in the natural light with direct access to backyard. Stainless steel appliances and snack bar area in living dining room are will  certainly excite you to host all of your upcoming holiday and family events. Single car garage features a new washer and dryer and the home features accordion and storm panels for your  convenience. Area amenities include: Community clubhouse includes outdoor BBQ area, community pool hot tub and more. Just a stone's through away you will find Dieke Park featuring  a beautiful jogging trail, playground and more. HOA APPLICATION
